summary: man I loved the Far From Home trailer as much as everyone else but I'm just really confused??? Peter is alive, Nick Fury and...
question: man I loved the Far From Home trailer as much as everyone else but I'm just really confused??? Peter is alive, Nick Fury and Maria Hill too?? I think it was her in that scene where Nick & a woman are shooting at the Sand man and I'm just like ?????? what the hell happened in Endgame man, everyone is so happy and there's no one acknowledging the snap let alone Peter's trauma in turning to dust. Maybe they'll talk about it in the movie but i'm just rly rly confused rn
answer: Well yeah they don’t want to give away anything that happens in Avengers: Endgame and I’m sure addressing the stuff that happened in Infinity War would do just that. There’s been the theory that they’re gonna go back in time and fix everything and I think that Marvel has even confirmed something about all the deaths being reversed? I forget some people still think they’re truly dead. At this point, I know they’re not going to stay that way. I’m just surprised they released the trailer already when not even Captain Marvel has come out yet. I bet they knew people were going to be confused. They’re just toying with our emotions at this point 😑

body:
that haunted look in peter’s eyes?

dont panic.

here peter realises whatever decision he makes next is gonna be the wrong one. he takes the suit and inevitably gets pulled into a fight whilst hes trying to take a break from the fight.

he doesnt take the suit and he has no way to protect his friends or himself if he decides to just go for it. hes deciding what to do realising hes a real hero now bc he cant have a break.
